title: Microsoft Azure PostgreSQL Database: Connections
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/azure
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the number of active and failed connections.
 You can configure levels using the rule "Database Connections".

item:
 The name of the resource.

discovery:
 One service is created for each database if any of required metrics
 (average_active_connections, total_connections_failed) are given.
